[CITE@@EN[XQuery 1.0 and XPath 2.0 Functions and Operators]] ([CODE[2007-01-19 07:02:42 +09:00]] 版) <http://www.w3.org/TR/2007/REC-xpath-functions-20070123/>
([[名無しさん]] [WEAK[2007-01-27 03:27:39 +00:00]])

